							<div class="panel-body">
								<ul>
									<li>During these challenging times, we are offering extra flexibility and support for all new reservations with flexi cancellation policy up to 24-hours prior to arrival for 2021.</li>
									<li>Our online portal is fully active for bookings with updated rates and offerings, and details on our cancellation policies</li>
								</ul>
