								<a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#spencesafeaccordion" href="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
									Arrivals and Departures                                        </a>
							</h4>
						</div>
						<div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading2">
							<div class="panel-body">
								<ul>
									<li>All guests will be subjected to temperature check prior to entering the resort</li>
									<li>If a guest shows temperature above 37.6 oC, he/she will be directed to local healthcare experts and upon confirmation of safety, will be escorted to the designated resort</li>
									<li>Our fleet of ground transport will be disinfected as per standards. Our designated chauffers will be equipped with mask and gloves; and will be confirmed safe with temperature checks and PCR tests</li>
