											<li>Travel history for last 21 days – International (which countries)</li>
											<li>If quarantined in any other country for last 30 days,
												<ul>
													<li>Certificate of completion of quarantine period</li>
													<li>reason for being quarantined (Close contact with COVID-19 patient or due to travel from High risk country/place, etc)</li>
												</ul>
											</li>
										</ul>
									</li>
									<li>As per safety guidelines, our welcome will be a traditional welcome with hands clasped. No handshakes will take place at the hotels/resorts</li>
