									<li>Welcome drink will be served in a sealed cup for your safety</li>
									<li>We encourage guests to inform Front Desk of checkout times 12-hours in advance to keep ready the necessary documentation to expedite processes</li>
									<li>We discourage the use of cash at checkout. A sanitised tray will be provided to place the credit card. Bills will be provided with sanitised pens for signature</li>
									<li>We discourage the use of paper bills. The bills will be emailed upon guest confirmation.</li>
								</ul>
								<p>Please note that mandatory daily temperature checks will be conducted for all guests and associates throughout their stay, at each outlet</p>
