							</h4>
						</div>
						<div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading4">
							<div class="panel-body">
								<ul>
									<li>Our accommodation unites have been sanitized and cleaned following health and safety protocols</li>
