							<div class="panel-body">
								<ul>
									<li>All team members will follow enhanced sanitation guidelines when conducting cleaning of all areas of the premises</li>
									<li>Our cleaning team will wear disposable masks, gloves and gowns when cleaning rooms or public areas, and will dispose of same in a pre-determined manner</li>
									<li>As with our guests, our team will also undergo daily temperature checks</li>
									<li>Reinforcement of personal hygiene measures through training</li>
									<li>Promoting frequent and effective handwashing and sanitation amongst all staff members</li>
									<li>Our kitchen team has undergone refresher training on food hygiene principals during curfew/lockdown period and follow ISO 22000/HACCP guidelines</li>
									<li>Physical distancing in the work environment / stations will be maintained and monitored</li>
									<li>Staff members are required to fill a health declaration form and keep the management informed of any illness or symptoms and not report for duty. To return to duty, such staff members are required to produce<br />
										negative PCR report confirmed by a professional healthcare worker</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="panel panel-default">
						<div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading9">
							<h4 class="panel-title">
								<a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#spencesafeaccordion" href="#collapse9" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse9">
									In Case Of Emergency                                        </a>
							</h4>
						</div>
